Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Polish propaganda
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wth2
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 10 Jan 1982
Trying to tell fact from fiction in reports coming from Poland under General Jaruzelski. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less